## Linear Algebra
## Problem 1.3.24 in Anton Elementary Linear Algebra, 10th edition
## ENDDESCRIPTION

## KEYWORDS('matrix')

## DBsubject('Linear Algebra')
## DBchapter('Matrices')
## DBsection('Matrix Operations')
